---
// Landing page with navbar and cards
import "../styles/tailwind.css";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="johncrow">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>The John Crow Project</title>
  </head>
  <body class="font-serif" data-current-page="home">
    <Navbar currentPage="home" />
    
    <main class="p-6 relative">
      <!-- Background image -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-30" style="background-image: url('/banner_johnchinaman.png');"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-base-content">
            The John Crow Project
          </h1>
          
          <p class="text-lg font-body text-base-content/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Documenting the history of anti-Chinese lynching, exclusion, and resistance<br>in the American West (1850 – 1915)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-12">
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="card-body p-2">
              <a href="/search" class="group">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <h2 class="card-title font-display text-sm text-base-content group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
                    Search Now
                  </h2>
                </div>
              </a>
              <p class="font-body text-base-content/70 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                Search through the archive with advanced filters and keywords.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="card-body p-2">
              <a href="/chat" class="group">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <h2 class="card-title font-display text-sm text-base-content group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
                    Ask a Question
                  </h2>
                </div>
              </a>
              <p class="font-body text-base-content/70 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                Chat with the archive using natural language queries.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="card-body p-2">
              <a href="/browse" class="group">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <h2 class="card-title font-display text-sm text-base-content group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
                    Browse the Records
                  </h2>
                </div>
              </a>
              <p class="font-body text-base-content/70 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                Browse the archive by location, date, or event type.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border border-base-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="card-body p-2">
              <a href="/visualize" class="group">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <h2 class="card-title font-display text-sm text-base-content group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
                    Visualize the Data
                  </h2>
                </div>
              </a>
              <p class="font-body text-base-content/70 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                See patterns and trends in the data through charts, maps, and timelines.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12 mb-8">
          <p class="font-body text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Welcome to John Crow Project, a webiste dedicated to restoring a forgotten chapter of American history—the relentless campaign of violence and legal exclusion that targeted Chinese immigrants across the West after the Gold Rush. Beginning in California’s goldfields in 1849, the terror spread eastward along wagon roads, rail lines, and river towns until, by the early 1900s, it had reached the Mississippi River and tragically intersected with the entrenched racial violence of Jim Crow. Drawing on newly compiled lynching databases, newspaper archives, and scholarship, this site traces how vigilante terror and discriminatory legislation worked hand-in-hand to drive Chinese communities from mines, rail camps, and towns.

          </p>
          
          <p class="font-body text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Here you'll find interactive maps of more than eighty documented lynchings and massacres, timelines that pair major exclusion laws with surges in mob violence, and primary-source collections that preserve the voices of victims, witnesses, and resisters. Our goal is to make this “red record” of the West impossible to ignore, to honor those who were lost, and to provide educators, descendants, and researchers the tools they need to confront the legacy of what we call <em>John Crow</em>—a western counterpart to Jim Crow that sought expulsion rather than segregation.

          </p>
          
          <p class="font-body text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed">
            Explore the evidence, contribute your family's stories, and help us extend this record—what you see here is a starting point, not an endpoint. Together we can uncover, verify, and map new cases and perspectives, transforming collective memory and advancing justice through truth.

          </p>
        </div>

        <footer class="text-center mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-base-300">
          <p class="text-sm font-body text-base-content/70">
            © Kevin Hegg, 2025. This website contains sensitive historical content. Please approach the material with respect and understanding of its historical context.
          </p>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  html,
  body {
    margin: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
</style>
